column1: MRI snapshot size (256, 128, 1) with weighting in T2 describing the skull of a man of age  of 37 years old, of axial section n°194 from the base of the skull. The image notably reveals the presence of: the white matter of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 32.9590 mm³, the cortex of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 1007.2266 mm³, the white matter of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 47.4609 mm³ and the cortex of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 958.4473 mm³.
